      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Storage layout design",
      "pos": [
        13357,
        13378
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To implement these strategies to implement the disk subsystem of the virtual machines with good performance, an IT workload or infrastructure typically takes advantage of many storage accounts.",
      "pos": [
        13380,
