      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This situation can add complexity to the management tasks.",
      "pos": [
        13697,
        13755
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Designing a sound strategy for storage, including appropriate naming for the underlying disks and associated VHD blobs is key.",
      "pos": [
